name: TextWrapModes
shortdesc: Options for wrapping text around an object.

property.name: JUMP_OBJECT_TEXT_WRAP
property.shortdesc: Forces text to jump above or below the object, so that no text appears on the object's right or left.

property.name: NEXT_COLUMN_TEXT_WRAP
property.shortdesc: Forces text to jump to the next available column.

property.name: BOUNDING_BOX_TEXT_WRAP
property.shortdesc: Wraps text around the object's bounding box.

property.name: CONTOUR
property.shortdesc: Wraps text around the object following the specified contour options.
